From:  David A. Moon <Moon@STONY-BROOK.SCRC.Symbolics.COM>
Line-fold:  No
Message-ID:  <19881102231403.2.MOON@EUPHRATES.SCRC.Symbolics.COM>
In-Reply-To:  <19881102220741.3.GREGOR@PORTNOY.parc.xerox.com>
